Race.SpecificTitle: Justice of the Peace -- Justice of the Peace District A
PW PJ Millage Renewal -- 1 Mill - PJ - 10 Yrs.
Race.FullText: Shall the Parish of Red River, State of Louisiana (the "Parish"), levy a special tax of one (1) mill on all the property subject to taxation within the Parish (an estimated $270,000 reasonably expected at this time to be collected from the levy of the tax for an entire year), for a period of ten (10) years, beginning with the year 2016 and ending with the year 2025, to acquire, construct, maintain and operate Parish Senior Citizens' Centers and to provide funding for Parish Senior Citizens' Programs, operated by the Red River Parish Council on Aging?
